# CODEOWNERS — Default reviewers for every Pull Request in this repository
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# This file is installed by Ahrena's `scripts/install.py` when the project
# selects the `github-codeowners` setup item. The installer resolves
# `{org}` from `git remote get-url origin`. Edit the team handle below if
# your repository's default code-owner is not `{org}/maintainers`.

* @{org}/maintainers
